<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3538">A Carabiner</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>It won't stop clicking&#8230; could this be a code</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Use</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">It&nbsp;fails.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
You throw the object at the wild Alces but it misses and hits a crow.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3604">A Crayfish</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>A soft buzzing goes off on your phone.</p>
<p>&quot;(1) New message from Craydaddy.&quot;</p>
<p>Weird.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Use</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;huh...&nbsp;at&nbsp;least&nbsp;it&nbsp;didn't&nbsp;pinch&nbsp;you</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>You set the crawfish on the ground. It charges toward Alces. He watches it and asks for its signature. The crayfish stops and begins to click its claws in delight before scuttling off.</p>
<p>&quot;Don't worry, it's grabbing enough so you can have its signature also.&quot;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4016">A Twine Man</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>It looks up at you before making a fighting stance.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Use</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">:oh&nbsp;no:</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
You chuck it at the author only to have it hit a butterfly. You stare on as the little twine man gets up. It looks up and races off after a mouse.</p>
<p>&quot;He doesn't really like harming anything that isn't a mouse&#8230;even then, that's subject to change.&quot; Alces watches the twine man before looking back at you.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4902">A Whole-ass Fridge with Alphabet Magnets</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>How can this fit in your fucking bag and not break it?!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Use</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I&nbsp;mean...&nbsp;what&nbsp;did&nbsp;you&nbsp;expect?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
You attempt to pull it out of your bag but, it's too heavy. The magnets on it move to form a message, &quot;no&quot;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4195">A Flower Bulb</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>It opens up and reveals a counciling panphlet.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Use</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">oof</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
You throw the flower by the bulb at Alces, it misses him and hits some random coder that made a discord bot.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/not-all-fiction-is-told">A Storybook</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>It's filled with strange markings.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Open</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">there's&nbsp;just&nbsp;one&nbsp;paper...and&nbsp;a&nbsp;lot&nbsp;of&nbsp;blank&nbsp;pages.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/penny-for-your-thoughts">A phone.</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/a-passed-away-pup">It's parchment, and has a cute dog drawn on there</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/not-all-fiction-is-told">A fairy tale book with a small golden tree on the cover</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/alces-statue-garden">A Sculpture</a></p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Close&nbsp;Info</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>You stare at it and hear a bird's tweeting.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Use</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">hmm</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
You chuck it at Alces, but he catches it and looks it over for scratches and marks.</p>
<p>&quot;Be careful, this is fragile clay and it took hours to make.&quot;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br /></blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none">
<p>You scan Alces figure before asking a question.</p>
<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;What&nbsp;is&nbsp;that&nbsp;carabiner&nbsp;doing?&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoiler</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>&quot;Morse code&#8230; I assume you're also curious about what it is too. Originally, it was supposed to be a funny article about a carabiner that was arrogant. The original I thought of would've been a climber that turned into a carabiner. Now though, it's a carabiner who's just trying to have people remember his last owner in the best way. Really and honestly, Uncle Nicolini, another wildish author who you can find shitposting around here, is the one who helped me through this entire process.&quot;</p>
<p>“Also there was a title spelling on the goddamn thing it was on main for one whole month! (maybe more)” he mutters under his breath.</p>
<p>Alces stares at you, awaiting the next question.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;What's&nbsp;up&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;Crayfish?&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>&quot;Once again, a sad article that was meant to be funny. To be honest, I'm somewhat shocked as to how something called &quot;Craydaddy,&quot; is on main. I got the idea when I rescued a crayfish. He was in a defensive stance that looked like a stereotypical rapper. I kept laughing and laughing until, I realized, that this would be a great article. Now, here we are talking about it.&quot;</p>
<p>Alces pauses and his eyes wander off to a river.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;Who&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;twine&nbsp;man&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Slight&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>&quot;Twine man, many things. My first collab, the second thing I wrote, a piece griping about the mice in my barn&#8230; In the end, I think that Zyn, the butterfly you just hit with it, was who helped mold it out. She gave me a critique on forums to which I tore down all of its dialogue and then rebuilt it from the start to make 4016 mute&#8230; She liked it and wanted to collab. We got right to work and sure enough, it was ready to post in, what like, two days? I think?&quot;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;What&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;world&nbsp;is&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;fridge?&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">No&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Jam Con, it was so satisfying to be able to create and post something on the same day as its creation. I strongly encourage everyone who is able to, join a contest! Also, it's my first just funny article.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;Anything&nbsp;important?&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Yeah.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>If I am uncontactable for 2 months on any platform then Yossi gets control over all articles I’ve written. Whether it be deleting, rewriting, image replacement, etc.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-2" style="display:none">
<p>Alces looks up wide-eyed before asking;</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;Cat?&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Shadow</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-wild-alces-alces-is-plugging/shadow.JPG" alt="shadow.JPG" class="image" /><br />
an evil mastermind at its purrest</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&quot;Dog?&quot;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Pinto</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-wild-alces-alces-is-plugging/pinto.JPG" alt="pinto.JPG" class="image" /><br />
zoom</div>
</div>
